Bitcoin Casino’s FAQ

What is a Bitcoin?

Bitcoin is a digital currency that exists only on the Internet. People use this cryptocurrency as a payment method for digital transactions. You may buy and trade Bitcoins or convert them into other currencies via online exchange services.

What is a Bitcoin casino?

Bitcoin casino is an online gambling platform that accepts cryptocurrency. On such sites, gamblers may play different types of games using BTC. The primary advantage of Bitcoin casinos over ordinary platforms is 100% safe, anonymous, and hassle-free gambling.

How can I win a Bitcoin?

You can earn Bitcoins by mastering and making wins in BTC games at 7BitCasino.

Do all online casinos accept Bitcoin?

No! Not all casinos deal with Bitcoin, but 7Bit does. We also accept other cryptocurrencies and fiat money.

Is Bitcoin a gamble?

No, it’s not! You can use Bitcoin for many purposes: purchasing food and stuff, paying bills, and gambling in BTC online casinos.

Is Bitcoin gambling legal?

It depends on a particular country and its gambling laws. For example in the USA, there is no official ban on Bitcoin casino gambling. At the same time, most districts have stringent regulations on gambling activities. Nevada remains the friendliest state in this regard by now.

Is Bitcoin safe to use for online gambling?

Yes. Bitcoin payments at crypto casinos are completely safe and transparent because they run via a peer-to-peer network, called a blockchain.
